snippet.title: Serious Sam Classic: The Second Encounter - Full Game Walkthrough (No Commentary Longplay)
snippet.description:
This longplay of Serious Sam: The Second Encounter includes the full campaign and all the boss fights and cutscenes in this full playthrough and is recorded in HD on the PC.

It's recorded without commentary so you can focus on the game itself. 

► Please subscribe if you liked, thanks!
